## What changed

Added three conditions to **skip** the re-read when user is saving, deleting, or refreshing:

| sy-ucomm | Action | Re-read? |
|---|---|---|
| 'SALEORD' or other | Dropdown changed | **Yes** — update display |
| 'SAVE' | User saving appointment | **No** — keep user's entered values |
| 'DELE' | User deleting appointment | **No** — keep current values for delete |
| 'REFRESH' | User clicked refresh | **No** — fields get cleared anyway |

